title: Wishlist 2025
text:
Welcome to my Birthday/Christmas wishlist website for the 2025 celebration season. Be sure to read all announcements on his home page, or else, you’re lame.
A couple ground rules to lay out. These can be either suggestions or inspirations. If you wish to take these as inspirations, and go on your merry creative way. Go ahead! If your name is Michael Kepler and you have a hard time expressing creativity during the Christmas festivities and can only provide athlectic gummies or stolen packages as presents, then you may take these as ideas if you so may wish.
For Mom and Dad to read: I do not expect much from either of you this year! You are already providing enough for me this year, so if you would look through this and pick one item out that is absolutely perfect! But I don’t want you to think this is all needed, as you have already given me everything I would ever need this year! #much love
For Michael: guh
For Mom-mom: Use this as ideas becuase I know you get stressed about picking things out! There are many different taps for each category of present, so use this as much as you want!
For Nick:



nhehehe


Happy reading through!
Much love, Margaret

title: About the CEO
text:
About the CEO



Welcome one, welcome all. Y’all know me but if you don’t, here are my stats.
Height: 6’7”
Accomplishments: Nobel Peace Prize, Pulitzer Prize
2k Time: 5:37.1
If you are intimidated, you should be. In the presence of greatness.
That is all, please proceed!

title: Miscellaneous
text: Greetings and welcome to the first section, Miscellaneous items! Down below you shall find an array of exquisite options, choose one that suits your fancy!

title: Miscellaneous
text:
Camera
I have recently become one with cherishing moments, and then printing them out to a cute and memorable photo album. Having a nice camera to capture these moments is something I would love to do! I’ve done the research, so below are some good options of which kind.

Sony Cyber-shot Dsc hx9v
Cannon SX740 HS
Also, easily researchable…

title: Miscellaneous
text:
Photo Album
Going along this same theme here, I am running out of room in my currrent photo album! A fun little colorful thing, with room on the ends to write in notes, would be amazing!

title: Clothes
text: As always, clothes are always incredibly welcome! I am a big fan of them. As I can be a picky little lady (as you always say, Mother) here are some of my favorite items as of late, use them as they are or use them as inspiration!

title: Clothes

title: Clothes
text:
Particular Items

Been really into jackets recently! A lot of cool looking jackets I saw at Zara and Free People in particular.
SWEATERS AS ALWAYS
i love some colorful little comfy scarves, big scarf girl recently
Some cute little shirts and long sleeves and what not, maybe some cute formal attire for internships! Been really into color tho, if you need any advice go to Nicholas as he is subjected to hearing and seeing every piece of clothing I even remotely fancy so if you need an opinion on an item for me, send him a picture he knows the answer
There are some nice long sleeves at zara, kind of a wider neck kind of look which was nice (makes my broad/so muscular shoulders look less big, can be applied to sweater too) but there was a nice green colored long sleeve that was cute
Cute colors, unique, idk cute things I been loving!
